
  Glalie    Ice Type Pokémon

  GLALIE has a body made of rock, 
  which it hardens with an armor 
  of ice.  Glalie has the 
  ability to freeze moisture in 
  the atmosphere into any shape 
  it desires. 
	Evolution Chain
      Snorunt ► Glalie

